          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Freeze all assets in China, including movable and immovable property and other types of assets",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "effect_type": "prohibit_transactions",
      "scope": "full",
      "description": [
        {
          "value": "禁止我国境内组织、个人与其进行有关交易、合作等活动",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Prohibit organizations and individuals in China from engaging in transactions, cooperation or related activities with the entity with the individual",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "effect_type": "visa_ban",
      "scope": "full",
      "description": [
        {
          "value": "对其不予签发签证、不准入境（包括香港、澳门）",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Visa ban and entry prohibition (including Hong Kong and Macao)",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "reasons": [
    {
      "category": "other",
      "description": [
        {
          "value": "公然同\"台独\"分裂势力勾连，严重违背一个中国原则和中日四个政治文件精神，严重干涉中国内政，严重损害中国主权和领土完整。",
          "lang": "zh",
          "script": "Hani",
          "is_primary": true
        },
        {
          "value": "Openly colluding with \"Taiwan independence\" separatist forces, seriously violating the One-China principle and the spirit of the four China-Japan political documents, seriously interfering in China's internal affairs, and seriously damaging China's sovereignty and territorial integrity.",
          "lang": "en",
          "script": "Latn",
          "is_primary": false
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
